          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-947BCWJS-line-1" n="1">
              <hi rend="display-initial">Y<hi rend="small-caps">OU</hi> always are making a God of your Spouse,</hi>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947BCWJS-line-2" n="2">But this neither Reason nor Conscience allows;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947BCWJS-line-3" n="3">Perhaps you will say, 'tis in Gratitude due,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947BCWJS-line-4" n="4">And you adore him, because he adores you.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947BCWJS-line-5" n="5">Your Argument's weak, and so you will find,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947BCWJS-line-6" n="6">For you, by this Rule, must adore all Mankind.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
